description: Returns a list of tags attached to the specified Amazon Lookout for Vision model. This operation requires permissions to perform the lookoutvision:ListTagsForResource operation.

parameters.name: ResourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model for which you want to list tags.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: A map of tag keys and values attached to the specified model.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: The key of the tag that is attached to the specified model.

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: The value of the tag that is attached to the specified model.
